---
summary: Messages should have linkable URLs
---
created: 2014-09-20 00:45:52.0
creator: matthew
description: "I'm seeing a lot of scenarios where it'd be really nice to be able to link to a given message.  E.g:\n\nitsnotmoi:\tgotcha. i wondered if clicking to an idle nick would take me to their last said thing but it takes me to their ID page\t\nMatthew: mm, having recent history on the ID page could be rather useful though - \"Foo was last seen at <foo> in #bar:baz.com - saying <clicky linked messages>\""
