- author: matthew
  body: |-
    I tried to clarify in the description.

    The ask here is to provide a URL schema in the client which lets you jump to specific messages - e.g. http://server/_matrix/client/#/message/<msgid> - or perhaps http://server/_matrix/client//#/room/!XqBunHwQIXUiqCaoxq:matrix.org/message/<msgid>, so i can say:

    "Kegan: what did you make of this convo? http://server/_matrix/client//#/room/!XqBunHwQIXUiqCaoxq:matrix.org/message/<msgid>"
